Minigun: Fires a high rate of bullets but with low damage.
Shotgun: Fires a destructive volley of shots that pushes back the enemy.
Plasma: Fires a plama beam piercing through enemies.
Flamer: Burns enemies to a crisp with napalm.
Shocker: Zaps enemies and chains to the nearest target.
Cryo: Freezes enemies for a short time with cyro spikes.
